scopecontent.p:
Includes printed typescript by "Terrel" [Hale], signed; printed typescript by Peter Middleton withnote by Middleton to Mandel attached; 
                        Furnitures
                      no. 9, sent to Mandel by editor Mark Nowak with an autograph letter, signed, by Nowak attached; printed typescript of poems by Carmen Lupton with an autograph letter, signed, attached; and printed typescript of poems by Daniel Davidson.
